      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstration that simulation input parameters match experimental conditions within stated uncertainty bounds for all QoI-sensitive inputs.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency assessment not performed. Shear-stress exponent used in simulation (α=0.785) sourced from 1990 literature; experimental conditions under which this value was derived differ from current test setup. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
